node.text: Have you tried the Damiki rig yet 💥? It’s a great alternative to a drop shot or a ned rig in these hot summer months. The head design allows your bait to sit completely level so you can vertical jig it, bottom hop it, and tight line it. Give it a shot to finesse those finicky summer fish! Found over at modernoutdoortackle.com
